# Task 21 – Project Demo Video Planning

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This document outlines the demonstration plan for showcasing the Smart Library Request Workflow application.

## Demo Includes

- Student Login
- Portal Walkthrough
- Borrow Request Submission
- Librarian Approval
- Flow Designer Automation
- Email Notification
- Status Tracking
- Book Return Process
- Most Borrowed Books Report

## Demo Roles

### Student

- Login
- Submit Borrow Request
- Track Request Status

### Librarian

- Approve Request
- Issue Book
- Return Book
- View Reports

## Estimated Duration

Approximately **8 minutes**

## Status

Completed
